WEBVTT

00:05.313 --> 00:08.550
Maybe one of your friends
would like to go home instead?

00:10.980 --> 00:12.781
They're coming in, I just opened the gate.

00:12.782 --> 00:13.978
- You let the cops in!
- What the fuck!

00:14.003 --> 00:15.745
I had no choice.
Gus was about to give us up.

00:15.770 --> 00:18.092
Go! Stop them! Stop!

00:19.440 --> 00:21.074
Come on!

00:21.075 --> 00:22.543
Hey, hey, look.

00:22.544 --> 00:23.598
Maybe we should just talk out here.

00:23.623 --> 00:26.547
Okay. What would you like to say?

00:26.548 --> 00:28.116
- Hey.
- Hello.

00:28.117 --> 00:30.784
- How are you?
- Good.

00:30.785 --> 00:32.686
What's going on, Gus?

00:32.686 --> 00:34.855
