00:34.856 --> 00:36.722
Um, is there a problem?

00:37.120 --> 00:39.151
He won't fit. He won't fit.

00:39.152 --> 00:40.518
Okay, okay.

00:40.519 --> 00:43.046
Hey, we're gonna cut off his feet.

00:43.071 --> 00:44.360
- What?
- Yeah, yeah.

00:44.385 --> 00:45.812
Go get the biggest knife you can find.

00:45.813 --> 00:46.841
- Oh, my God.
- Do it!

00:46.842 --> 00:48.876
We have started an official investigation

00:48.877 --> 00:50.711
into the-the missing boat.

00:50.712 --> 00:52.847
Yeah, we... but we told you,

00:52.848 --> 00:54.815
uh, that we didn't know
anything about any boat.

00:54.816 --> 00:56.955
Oh? Because your friend seemed to think

00:56.956 --> 00:58.337
you might be able to help.

00:58.338 --> 01:00.735
Help... help answer any questions.

01:00.760 --> 01:03.762
Didn't know exactly what and, again,

01:03.763 --> 01:06.732
we don't anything about a missing boat.

01:07.459 --> 01:09.167
That's perfect. All right, you got him?

01:09.168 --> 01:11.470
- Okay.
- Wait.

01:11.471 --> 01:14.205
- Wouldn't it be quicker to...
- What?

01:14.206 --> 01:16.074
- No.
- What?

01:16.075 --> 01:17.976
- No.
- What?!

01:17.977 --> 01:20.039
Cut off his head?

01:20.064 --> 01:21.613
Yeah. Okay, yeah.

01:21.614 --> 01:24.117
Great, okay.
Okay.

01:24.142 --> 01:24.718
Ready? Here we go.

01:24.743 --> 01:25.876
- One...
- Ugh.

01:25.877 --> 01:27.911
Ah, I can't do it!

01:27.912 --> 01:30.046
Maybe we can talk inside.

01:30.047 --> 01:31.515
Uh, but I know you said,

01:31.516 --> 01:34.418
um, you wanted to speak to Milo, right?

01:34.419 --> 01:36.453
But, uh, he's not back yet,

01:36.454 --> 01:38.355
and the other guys went to bed,

01:38.356 --> 01:42.193
so why don't we just, uh, talk out here?

