26:54.426 --> 26:55.559
Put this down, put this down.

26:55.560 --> 26:56.441
Careful, careful.

26:56.442 --> 26:57.972
Shit.

26:57.997 --> 26:59.211
Hey, come on.

26:59.212 --> 27:00.212
