27:25.685 --> 27:27.520
- Are they coming over here?
- What?

27:27.872 --> 27:28.738
Are they coming over here?

27:28.739 --> 27:31.208
Yep. They're coming here.

27:34.244 --> 27:35.614
Hey, there.

27:36.480 --> 27:37.795
Isn't this special?

27:37.796 --> 27:39.023
Oh, yeah.

27:39.024 --> 27:41.451
Proves you're alive, huh?

27:42.293 --> 27:44.560
Can you believe this full moon?

27:44.561 --> 27:46.362
You don't get this up in the States.

27:46.363 --> 27:48.731
Don't look at it.

27:48.732 --> 27:50.063
Don't fucking look at it.

27:50.064 --> 27:52.269
So where you guys from?

27:56.575 --> 27:58.211
Vancouver.

28:01.481 --> 28:03.886
- Great boat.
- Yeah, thanks.

28:03.887 --> 28:06.419
- Thank you.
- You, too.

28:13.693 --> 28:16.495
What do you say we don't
tell anybody about this?

28:16.496 --> 28:19.632
Well, folks come down here
and spoil it, huh?

28:23.833 --> 28:25.368
Well...

28:26.969 --> 28:28.771
see you around.

28:48.075 --> 28:49.809
- Let's get him out!
- Yeah, yeah, yeah.

28:49.810 --> 28:51.043
- Let's get him out quick.
- We need a...

28:51.044 --> 28:52.412
I'll get a thing.

28:52.413 --> 28:54.481
Get the-the stick, the pole,

28:54.482 --> 28:56.349
- the pole with the...
- A gaff!

28:56.350 --> 28:57.584
- Get a gaff.
- A gaff, a gaff.

28:57.585 --> 29:00.354
Get a coat hanger or something.

29:19.713 --> 29:22.147
Look, even if we do find the right one,

29:22.148 --> 29:24.329
are you gonna be able to sail
this thing back in the dark?

29:24.330 --> 29:27.221
Yes. We're gonna do this.

29:29.052 --> 29:30.719
