we find the one that works.

29:33.231 --> 29:34.427
- All right.
- Okay.

29:39.825 --> 29:41.561
Nope.

29:45.029 --> 29:47.028
Yep, try it.

29:47.216 --> 29:49.299
Lex, try it!

29:49.300 --> 29:50.901
