30:09.002 --> 30:10.503
Yeah!

30:15.516 --> 30:16.950
- Yeah!
- All right!

30:16.951 --> 30:18.284
We just fixed a boat, man.

30:18.285 --> 30:19.522
Yes, we did.

30:19.547 --> 30:20.887
- Yeah.
- All right.

30:20.888 --> 30:22.045
Okay, it's-it's got to be

30:22.070 --> 30:23.763
