31:17.359 --> 31:19.569
- What letter?
- Four years ago, my big break.

31:19.570 --> 31:22.122
All Mr. Big Shot here had to do was

31:22.123 --> 31:24.661
write a simple letter
of recommendation, you know.

31:24.662 --> 31:26.575
