31:47.135 --> 31:49.070
Mikey McFarlane was just in Grand Rapids

31:49.071 --> 31:53.009
and he told me how you
fucked me, college buddy.

31:59.516 --> 32:01.416
You have any idea what happened to me

32:01.417 --> 32:02.757
