32:12.278 --> 32:14.246
for what I wrote

32:14.247 --> 32:17.297
because you went back
to drinking and drugging

32:17.922 --> 32:19.957
for God knows how many years,
so I would say

32:19.958 --> 32:23.958
that unreliable is a pretty
accurate description.

32:24.529 --> 32:27.465
