33:28.954 --> 33:32.190
Can I suggest

33:32.191 --> 33:33.992
for now

33:33.993 --> 33:36.390
you accept his apology

33:37.597 --> 33:41.597
and we can at least try to

33:41.801 --> 33:45.770
make this deadline that is now just-just-

33:45.771 --> 33:48.741
