34:34.085 --> 34:36.219
Um...

34:36.219 --> 34:38.909
this is just my opinion,

34:39.723 --> 34:41.067
but...

34:42.458 --> 34:45.596
I don't think we're gonna
make the deadline now.

34:47.731 --> 34:48.904
Right.

34:50.467 --> 34:53.835
Again, just my opinion,

34:53.837 --> 34:57.837
